Package burlap.oomdp.stochasticgames.common

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgentFactoryWithSubjectiveReward
    An agent generating factory that will produce an agent that uses an internal subjective reward function.
    ConstantSGStateGenerator
    A stochastic games state generator that always returns the same base state, which is specified via the constructor.
    StaticRepeatedGameActionModel
    This action model can be used to take a single stage game, and cause it to repeat itself.
    VisualWorldObserver
    A WorldObserver that visualizes each transition with a fixed refresh delay between when the transition is rendered and when control is returned to the client.
